{"tid":449490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港動畫師幫國際知名遊戲品牌製作動畫影片","createTime":"2017-10-27T08:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T08:31:13.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc0f25ade283b8c971c33b52398576240ed2933","tid":449490,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T08:27:12.000Z","msg":"【特約轉播】只要有機會  香港動畫都可以好高質<br />\n<br />\n其實只要肯畀機會，香港都可以有好嘅創作，就好似以下呢條由一間本地小型廣告公司夥拍一班90後動畫師幫國際遊戲品牌UBISOFT製作嘅動畫影片，就算唔係神級都叫得做國際水平，睇完成個人都好熱血，與其大家慨嘆香港冇好嘅創意作品，倒不如真心支持吓佢哋更加實際。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲：《刺客教條：起源》<br />\n影片來源： Ubisoft<br />\n廣告公司： 朝日創作 Rise Creation<br />\n動畫製作： Paperbox Creations<br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/1712697322097278/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F1712697322097278%2F&d=eUE%2BeL1Xlivs6JdDGUmlLi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e79a7b32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/1712697322097278/</a>"},{"pid":"6a418a83eca5da914e7b4b6f96508b9537c59ec3","tid":449490,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"Ubisoft trailer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc05f286f193ae45db511a2ec9d805426270edb","tid":449490,"uid":20352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ubisoft trailer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雷聲大降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1596783f4190dd92b281c0ace211dbc05fd50ae","tid":449490,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ubisoft trailer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass